    "title": "Israel forcibly displaces more Palestinian families in East Jerusalem",
    "url": "https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/3/25/israel-forcibly-displaces-more-palestinian-families-in-east-jerusalem?traffic_source=rss",
    "publishTime": "2026-03-25T18:29:50.000Z",
