    "title": "Repeat offender with long rap sheet allegedly guns down man while free on probation, bonds despite violations",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/us/repeat-offender-long-rap-sheet-allegedly-guns-down-man-while-free-probation-bonds-despite-violations",
