    "title": "NJ Gov. Sherrill attends mosque led by Imam once accused of Hamas ties in deportation case",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/politics/nj-gov-sherrill-attends-mosque-led-imam-once-accused-hamas-ties-deportation-case",
