    "title": "Vince Vaughn calls out late-night shows all feeling 'the same,' becoming 'agenda-based' scolding",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/media/vince-vaughn-calls-out-late-night-shows-all-feeling-the-same-becoming-agenda-based-scolding",
