    "title": "Kristin Cavallari slams ‘trash’ married athletes for ‘scumbag’ social media behavior",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/kristin-cavallari-slams-trash-married-athletes-scumbag-social-media-behavior",
