    "title": "Caitlin Clark earns Diana Taurasi’s approval after wearing iconic No 12 for Team USA debut",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/sports/caitlin-clark-earns-diana-taurasis-approval-after-wearing-iconic-no-12-team-usa-debut",
    "publishTime": "2026-03-24T20:20:37.000Z",
