    "title": "Democrat strategist warns Mamdani's ballooning NYC budget plan gives Republicans a ready-made midterm message",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/media/democrat-strategist-warns-mamdanis-ballooning-nyc-budget-plan-gives-republicans-ready-made-midterm-message",
