    "title": "Charles Barkley delivers stern message to parents who don't 'whoop' their kids: 'Believe in discipline'",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/sports/charles-barkley-delivers-stern-message-parents-who-dont-whoop-kids-i-believe-discipline",
