    "title": "Polls open in key Denmark elections clouded by Trump’s Greenland threat",
    "url": "https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2026/3/24/polls-open-in-key-denmark-elections-clouded-by-trumps-greenland-threat?traffic_source=rss",
