    "title": "Joe Rogan rips Gavin Newsom for mocking Nick Shirley over his 'billion dollar' fraud investigations",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/media/joe-rogan-rips-gavin-newsom-mocking-nick-shirley-over-his-billion-dollar-fraud-investigations",
