    "title": "California cemetery removes banner draped over 9/11 memorial advertising new Islamic section after backlash",
    "url": "https://www.foxnews.com/media/california-cemetery-removes-banner-draped-over-9-11-memorial-advertising-new-islamic-section-after-backlash",
